    \"startedAt\": 1773173290896,\n      \"endedAt\": 1773173368291\n    }\n  ],\n  \"text\": \"active subagents:\\n(none)\\n\\nrecent (last 5m):\\n1. 小说评审-人物分析师 (glm-5, 1m) failed - 阅读 /root/.openclaw/workspace/memory/novel-reviews/prompt-2026-03-10T20-0...\\n2. 小说评审-设定管理员 (glm-5, n/a) failed - 阅读 /root/.openclaw/workspace/memory/novel-reviews/prompt-2026-03-10T20-0...\\n3. 小说评审-逻辑审核员 (glm-5, 1m, tokens 11k (in 8.6k / out 2.2k), prompt/cache 12k) done - 阅读 /root/.openclaw/workspace/memory/novel-reviews/prompt-2026-03-10T20-0...\"\n}"}],"details":{"status":"ok","action":"list","requesterSessionKey":"agent:main:cron:146083a3-dae7-409d-86cc-6a953d1cbdd6","callerSessionKey":"agent:main:cron:146083a3-dae7-409d-86cc-6a953d1cbdd6","callerIsSubagent":false,"total":3,"active":[],"recent":[{"index":1,"runId":"5e5e4fa1-2427-4e1a-a9f2-e0654fd5a1ab","sessionKey":"agent:main:subagent:48d5c5d1-8ca5-4d00-a941-8c6a2bf5117d","label":"小说评审-人物分析师","task":"阅读 /root/.openclaw/workspace/memory/novel-reviews/prompt-2026-03-10T20-0...","status":"failed","runtime":"1m","runtimeMs":2948,"model":"zai/glm-5","startedAt":1773173334254,"endedAt":1773173337202},{"index":2,"runId":"36e1610b-9ba3-422c-81c4-2c9f071f77ac","sessionKey":"agent:main:subagent:cc6bc21c-26a7-48dd-96b6-72e679d832b7","label":"小说评审-设定管理员","task":"阅读 /root/.openclaw/workspace/memory/novel-reviews/prompt-2026-03-10T20-0...","status":"failed","runtime":"n/a","runtimeMs":-2109,"model":"zai/glm-5","startedAt":1773173314475,"endedAt":1773173312366},{"index":3,"runId":"e0a89d67-5ae4-4226-a722-e784218a10b5","sessionKey":"agent:main:subagent:f2980ea4-e485-47a3-ba5a-6cd559d1ba3f","label":"小说评审-逻辑审核员","task":"阅读 /root/.openclaw/workspace/memory/novel-reviews/prompt-2026-03-10T20-0...","status":"done","runtime":"1m","runtimeMs":77395,"model":"zai/glm-5","totalTokens":12053,"startedAt":1773173290896,"endedAt":1773173368291}],"text":"active subagents:\n(none)\n\nrecent (last 5m):\n1. 小说评审-人物分析师 (glm-5, 1m) failed - 阅读 /root/.openclaw/works